name: Beanbang #20
description: Bean is a young man who really likes the nightlife. It was a powerful way to escape for a moment from reality. Bean uses clubbing activities as a means to meet friends and find a new atmosphere. According to him, he used to do it all when his feelings were in turmoil or he was having problems, of course, without being separated from alcoholic drinks. The atmosphere of hedonism is immediately inhaled when you enter, the upbeat music and the disco lights that illuminate the entire room are her joy.
